name: The Walking Dead Lands - Degenerative Walkers

metadata.name: Stage 01: DW-S1-B8J6P
metadata.description: A new subject added to the pool of Stage 01 walkers. We discovered several new ones lately, perhaps an unknown community was overrun. Decomposition has started and level of aggression is comparable to others. The subject did not react to any of the injections. We will proceed to a second round of exams tomorrow. [End of Report]
